  "status": "Stagnant",
  "summary": "This standard is an extension of [EIP-721](./eip-721.md). It introduces lockable NFTs. The locked asset can be used in any way except by selling and/or transferring it. The owner or operator can lock the token. When a token is locked, the unlocker address (an EOA or a contract) is set. Only the unlocker is able to `unlock` the token.",
  "title": "Lockable Extension for EIP-721"
